attachments.title: Paint The Town TEDxPortland 6K Night Run
attachments.text: Jump off the couch and join us for the inaugural TEDxPortland 6K Night Run on May 7th. Expect the unexpected with uniquely Portland surprises along the way. Lets paint the town TEDx with Gregory Gourdet as the honorary Marshall, the Unipiper, Gay Men&rsquo;s Chorus and more! FREE red NIKE Dri-FIT TEDxPortland shirt with registration for you to wear during the run!
